SDTM terminology codelists' definitions

Source: R/code_lists.R
cl_definitions.Rd

cl_definitions() returns the set of possible codelists' definitions.

Usage

cl_definitions(extensible = c("any", "yes", "no"))

Arguments

extensible

Should the returned value be restricted to codelists that are extensible ("yes"), not extensible ("no"), or both ("any").

Value

A character vector of codelists' definitions.

Examples

# `cl_definitions()` is the same as `cl_definitions(extensible = "any")`
cl_definitions()
